<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Ownership Transfer OTP - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #673AB7; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">üîê Ownership Transfer Verification</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

    <p>You have initiated an ownership transfer for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong>.</p>

    <div style="background: #f3e5f5; padding: 30px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Your One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
      <div style="font-size: 48px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #673AB7; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
        {{otpCode}}
      </div>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">This code expires in {{expiresIn}}</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #ffebee; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Warning:</strong><br>
        - This OTP can only be used once<br>
        - You have 3 attempts to enter the correct code<br>
        - Never share this code with anyone<br>
        - If you didn't request this transfer, ignore this email and contact support immediately
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Transfer Details:</strong></p>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Store:</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{storeName}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>New Owner Email:</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{newOwnerEmail}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Expires:</strong></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #f44336; font-weight: bold;">{{otpExpiresAt}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p><strong>What happens after verification?</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your role will change from Owner to Admin</li>
      <li>The new owner will gain full ownership rights</li>
      <li>Both parties will receive confirmation emails</li>
      <li>This action cannot be undone automatically</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      If you have questions or concerns, contact us at support@originfoodhouse.com
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
